missionSettings.description:
Escalation with extra sauce. Respawn rate of ground and air assets is increased. 

All naval assets are availible from the start and have been deployed in strategic positions.

Added defences, supplies and depots at some locations.

Increased amount of ground units for both factions (>120 each side).

Changed city airbases and slightly changed others for more interesting battles.

Victory is achieved when all enemy aircraft factories are destroyed.

(Beware, that Player has max level + increased starting funds and for every player on a team, the number of AI aircraft is reduced by 2 for friendly team and increased by 2 for the enemy)

Data.StringValue: The enemy has capitulated. We are victorious!
